title: Ready to go Home in Tacoma. 3 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ['Located in Lakewood, this 3-bd home is close to everything.', " With mid-century styling, updates in the the baths & kitchen, this gem is one you don't want to miss.", ' You will love the family room off the kitchen where everyone will gather for those memorable occasions.', 'So nice to have a formal LR and DR to do the big entertaining.', '(HW UNDER MOST OF THE CARPET).', 'Air conditioning makes the home comfortable & the sunroom makes the winters tolerable.', 'All bedrooms are generous in size & separate from the living areas.', 'The private backyard will give you a great place to relax or putz around.', 'The garage has built-ins, a workshop AND plenty of room for two cars.', 'Close to freeway access, shopping and medical services.', 'NO STAIRS-VERY APPEALING TO ALL!', '***Please Text & Call', 'show contact info', 'For More Details & Pics***']
